import React from 'react'
import Formfield from '../components/Formfield'

const Signup = () => {
  return (
    <form className="signup">
        <Formfield name="Name" label="Name" error=""  options={undefined} type="text"/>
        <Formfield name="Sex" label="Sex" error=""  options={["male", "female", "other"]} type="select"/>
        <Formfield name="password" label="Password"  error="" options={undefined} type="password"/>
        <Formfield name="email" label="Email"  error="" options={undefined} type="email"/>
        <Formfield name="dob" label="Year Of Birth"  error="" options={undefined} type="number"/>
    </form>
  )
}

export default Signup
